{i:0;a:4:{s:4:"type";s:16:"constructor_base";s:2:"id";s:5:"24618";s:4:"sort";s:2:"20";s:4:"text";s:2191:"<p>Patients from all over the world come to our clinic for ART treatment. We fully understand that you have to make additional efforts to arrange your treatment abroad and we are very grateful for your choice. It is our wish to try and make your stay in Saint-Petersburg less troublesome and easy to organize. </p>
<p>On one of the floors of our clinic, we offer comfortable wards equipped with a private bathroom, a double bed, a fridge, an air-conditioner, a TV-set and Wi-Fi. Couples can stay together and enjoy the combination of comfort and proximity to the whole range of medical services necessary to the patients during their IVF treatment.</p>
<p>The necessity to follow some simple rules within the regimen of the clinic will not prevent you from seeing Saint-Petersburg, the city entitled the <a href="https://www.worldtravelawards.com/award-worlds-leading-cultural-city-destination-2016">World\'s Leading Cultural City Destination 2016</a> and 2017 and <a href="https://www.worldtravelawards.com/award-europes-leading-heritage-destination-2018">Europe\'s Leading Heritage Destination 2018</a>. Saint-Petersburg will be waiting to show you its famous museums, magnificent palaces, spacious parks, beautiful bridges and gorgeous suburbs. The variety of concert and theatre life in the city can satisfy any taste. Our quiet rooms and a possibility to receive information and care from our friendly personnel at any time of your stay as well as positive emotions from sightseeing can serve very well to make you enjoy yourself and escape the unnecessary worries.</p>
<p>The prices for our wards are lower than for the hotel rooms and are not subject to change during high tourist seasons:
<ul>
<li>3,500 rubles a night for 1 person (breakfast, lunch and dinner included);<li>
<li>4,500 rubles a night for 2 persons (breakfast, lunch and dinner included).</li>
</ul></p>
<p>In order to stay in our comfortable ward, one will have to present some medical test results. For more information and for booking, please send your enquiry to <a href="mailto:trukhina@mcrm.ru">trukhina@mcrm.ru</a>. Please pay attention, as we are not a hotel we cannot provide you with visa support.</p>";}i:1;a:10:{s:4:"type";s:18:"constructor_header";s:2:"id";s:5:"24617";s:4:"sort";s:2:"10";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:5:"title";s:48:"Accommodation in ICRM for international patients";s:5:"image";b:0;s:12:"contact_name";N;s:11:"contact_job";N;s:13:"contact_phone";N;s:12:"contact_mail";N;}i:2;a:6:{s:4:"type";s:23:"constructor_slider_full";s:2:"id";s:5:"24619";s:4:"sort";s:2:"30";s:5:"title";N;s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:5:"items";a:8:{i:0;a:1:{s:15:"PREVIEW_PICTURE";a:8:{s:8:"ORIGINAL";s:59:"/upload/iblock/265/4a15b5e2967f2792332bd827e4cc5036_min.jpg";s:13:"webp_ORIGINAL";s:82:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/265/0_0_1_95/4a15b5e2967f2792332bd827e4cc5036_min.webp";s:20:"slider_photo_preview";s:82:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/265/279_223_1/4a15b5e2967f2792332bd827e4cc5036_min.jpg";s:25:"webp_slider_photo_preview";s:86:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/265/279_223_1_95/4a15b5e2967f2792332bd827e4cc5036_min.webp";s:25:"specialist_detail_preview";s:82:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/265/279_223_1/4a15b5e2967f2792332bd827e4cc5036_min.jpg";s:30:"webp_specialist_detail_preview";s:86:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/265/279_223_1_95/4a15b5e2967f2792332bd827e4cc5036_min.webp";s:17:"slider_popup_full";s:59:"/upload/iblock/265/4a15b5e2967f2792332bd827e4cc5036_min.jpg";s:22:"webp_slider_popup_full";s:87:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/265/1024_787_1_95/4a15b5e2967f2792332bd827e4cc5036_min.webp";}}i:1;a:1:{s:15:"PREVIEW_PICTURE";a:8:{s:8:"ORIGINAL";s:59:"/upload/iblock/599/5f20ea31c47f252e5ea27bfbf2537d8d_min.jpg";s:13:"webp_ORIGINAL";s:82:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/599/0_0_1_95/5f20ea31c47f252e5ea27bfbf2537d8d_min.webp";s:20:"slider_photo_preview";s:82:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/599/279_223_1