6:"constructor_base";s:2:"id";s:5:"27125";s:4:"sort";s:2:"20";s:4:"text";s:965:"<p>Payments for the <a target="_blank" href="/services/">medical services</a> provided in&nbsp;ICRM have to&nbsp;be&nbsp;made in&nbsp;the Russian rubles. </p>
<ul>
  <li>by&nbsp;cash or&nbsp;by&nbsp;a&nbsp;bank card in&nbsp;the ICRM cashier office with a&nbsp;printed receipt;</li>
  <li>by&nbsp;bank transfer to&nbsp;the ICRM bank account.</li>
</ul>
<p><a target="_blank" href="/upload/iblock/557/requisites_mcrm_eng.pdf">Our contact and bank details</a></p>
<p>Please pay attention:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Only bank cards registered for the payer name can be&nbsp;used for payment in&nbsp;ICRM. </li>
  <li>Bank cards registered not for the payer name cannot be&nbsp;accepted. </li>
  <li>To&nbsp;make a&nbsp;refund, personal presence of&nbsp;a&nbsp;payeer with his/her bank card that was used for the payment, the contract, in&nbsp;which he/she was mentioned as&nbsp;a&nbsp;payeer, or&nbsp;a&nbsp;notarized authorization from him/her are required.</li>
</ul>";}i:1;a:4:{s:4:"type";s:16:"constructor_base";s:2:"id";s:5:"27132";s:4:"sort";s:2:"40";s:4:"text";s:651:"<p>IVF cost include:</p>
<ul>
  <li>ultrasound scans during ovulation induction;</li>
  <li>ovarian puncture;</li>
  <li>preparation of&nbsp;sperm for fertilization;</li>
  <li>egg fertilization;</li>
  <li>embryo culture;</li>
  <li>embryo transfer into the uterine cavity.</li>
</ul>
<p>In&nbsp;the case some stages of&nbsp;IVF procedure are not performed the unused amount of&nbsp;money will be&nbsp;refunded.</p>
<p>For ICRM IVF patients the procedure is&nbsp;free of&nbsp;charge:</p>
<ul>
